attributes.Long form description: The student begins by taking the adapter and rotating the furniture, the instructions indicate that he must unscrew all the bolts and disassemble the furniture, then the student unscrews, removes and stores the first bolts, removes the first legs, and the base, finally finishes unscrew the rest of the legs, keeping the last bolts, separating the base of the same and thus finishing the task.
